				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$p\ll 0.001$$\end{document}p≪0.001). Similar effects are shown for both temperature (0.3  week/°C) and average precipitation (0.5 week/mm) (Supplementary Table 1).

